THE WORK IS PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND. It is a stylised
techno-economic model intended for directional analysis, not precise prediction
(see the accuracy summary in model_documentation.md).

Third-party data: the cost and weather *inputs* are derived from the external sources
cited in model_documentation.md (Lazard, NREL, ECMWF/ERA5, BloombergNEF, EIA, IPCC, EU
ETS, and others), each of which carries its own terms; this license covers the model and
its own outputs, not those third-party source materials.
